item.title: COOKING
item.description: For cooking, I’m willing to try, taste, and feel. It brings different colors and flavors to me every day.

item.title: PHOTOGRAPHY
item.description: “To me, photography is an art of observation. It’s about finding something interesting an ordinary place… I’ve found it has little to do with the things you see and everything to do with the way you see them.” — Elliott Erwitt
